## State Management
- Use Preact Safe React Signals for reactive UI updates
- Implement consent-driven data sharing with granular controls
- Create privacy-preserving state patterns that limit data exposure

## Performance Optimization
- Use client components only for direct user interaction
- Implement lightweight visualizations for financial data
- Optimize loading states for psychological safety

## Psychological Safety Considerations
- Use non-judgmental language throughout the platform
- Implement positive reinforcement messaging
- Include "don't know yet" options in all assessments
- Balance analytics with supportive content
- Make all data collection transparent and consensual

Follow these guidelines to create a platform that effectively serves both the financial management and emotional well-being needs of users.